# Policy

- No third-party libraries unless explicitly approved.
- Allowed by default: Apple system frameworks and SDKs.

# Adding a Dependency

- Add justification, security review, maintenance plan, and removal strategy.
- Pin versions; prefer minimal surface area.

# Prohibited

- Dynamic code loading, obfuscated binaries, abandoned libraries.
